snippet.title: Salt & Sacrifice multiplayer gameplay features - Future Games Show GamesCom 2021
snippet.description: James Silva from Ska Studios provided an overview of Salt and Sacrifice's online factions during the Future Games Show at Gamescom. Salt and Sacrifice is coming to PlayStation and PC in 2022.
